<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA524_08_IH_0001_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema524_08.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema524_08_ih_0001">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y">곱의 소수점 위치가 달라지는 규칙을 이용하여 <span class="empty_box nemo"></span> 안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center">
          <div class="flex dir_col gap_40">
            <div class="flex align_center">
              <span>3.14×1=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="3.14"></math-field></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex align_center">
              <span>3.14×10=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="31.4"></math-field></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex align_center">
              <span>3.14×100=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="314"></math-field></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex align_center">
              <span>3.14×1000=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="3140"></math-field></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex dir_col gap_40">
            <div class="flex align_center">
              <span>260×1=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="260"></math-field></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex align_center">
              <span>260×0.1=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="26"></math-field></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex align_center">
              <span>260×0.01=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="2.6"></math-field></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex align_center">
              <span>260×0.001=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="0.26"></math-field></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p class="text_bullet" lang="y">곱하는 수의 0이 하나씩 늘어날 때마다 곱의 소수점이 오른쪽으로 한 자리씩 옮겨집니다.</p>
                <p class="text_bullet" lang="y">곱하는 수의 소수점 아래 자리 수가 하나씩 늘어날 때마다 곱의 소수점이 왼쪽으로 한 자리씩 옮겨집니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- <div class="buttons_solve">
                  
              </div> -->
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
